    {
      "id": "1b34750c-f3ba-8055-b913-d01e1d323d95",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The aim of the approach is to make recommendations to each learner on courses they may wish to take. No comment on whether the effectiveness of the recommender is mentioned in the abstract. ",
